M: I met a cool Russian guy on­line. I want to
make friends with him.
W: Doesn’t he speak English?
M: Yes, his English is very good. But I think if
I learn Russian, I can understand him
better.
W: I agree. If you use Russian, he’ll feel much
closer to you.
M: In addition, speaking Russian can be an
advantage in my future career.
W:
